claim.claim-text:
1. A method for operating a technical facility with an expert system (1) for diagnosing (9) the operating state of the technical facility (2) characterized by the following steps: 
a) in the expert system (1), a malfunction is identified, automatically triggering a regulating intervention in the technical facility; 
b) at least one knowledge base (WB) available in the expert system is used—in parallel with the diagnosis (9)—to establish the regulating intervention (u); 
c) the regulating intervention (u) in the technical facility is continued until the system deviation (e) lies in a specified tolerance band.
